<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Case Registration</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header class="mt-4">
            <img src="/assets/das.png" alt="DAS Logo">
            <h1 class="display-4">Case Registration</h1>
            <nav class="breadcrumb">
                <ol class="breadcrumb">
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item active">1. Start Registration</li>
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item">2. Your Case & Documents</li>
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item">3. Your Information</li>
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item">4. Summary</li>
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item">5. Submit</li>
                </ol>
            </nav>
        </header>

        <section class="my-4">
            <h2>Start Registration</h2>
            <div class="alert alert-info">
                <h4 class="alert-heading">Important Information</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Collision damage? <a href="#">Report your case with collision damage here</a></li>
                    <li>Mass damage? Is your case part of mass damage? <a href="#">Report your mass damage case here</a></li>
                    <li>Entrepreneur? <a href="#">Report your business case here</a></li>
                    <li>Faster registration? Have your policy number, policy sheet, and contact details of your intermediary at hand.</li>
                    <li>Attachments are not mandatory in this form: you can always submit them later.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>Registering your case takes 10-15 minutes.</p>

            <form action="/step2" method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Does your conflict involve an amount higher than â‚¬175?</label>
                    <div class="custom-radio-group">
                        <div class="custom-radio">
                            <input type="radio" name="amountConflict" id="yes" value="Yes" required>
                            <label for="yes">Yes</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="custom-radio">
                            <input type="radio" name="amountConflict" id="no" value="No">
                            <label for="no">No</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="custom-radio">
                            <input type="radio" name="amountConflict" id="unknown" value="Don't know / Not applicable">
                            <label for="unknown">Don't know / Not applicable</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="caseType">What is your case about?</label>
                    <select class="form-control" id="caseType" name="caseType" required>
                        <option value="">-- Make your choice --</option>
                        <option value="collisionDamage">Collision Damage</option>
                        <option value="massDamage">Mass Damage</option>
                        <option value="business">Business Legal Issue</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Next &rarr;</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">Finish later</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>Made by <a href="https://digilize.de">Digilize Agency</a></p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
